data.description: Here's an Impressive 2-story, 5-bedroom 3 full bath home located in the prime community of Rolling Creek. Where the lights will never go out. Why, because the grid is a part of the emergency service power grid. The features in this home include a guest bedroom/mother-in-law suite downstairs, with an adjacent bathroom. This beautiful home won't disappoint as it provides a large open kitchen, granite tops, backsplash and loads of cabinet space. Find a casual dining & family room with an open concept even desk nook. Upstairs provides an addition large living area, for entertaining or movie nights. Conveniently located to The Forum shopping & dining. This home also provides energy efficient features making this home one to be desired. Big Texas size back yard provides ample space to entertain or add that swimming pool you've always wanted. Come out and take a look today.
